00:06:06,627 --> 00:06:08,988
And then the final one is the faculty of

67
00:06:09,644 --> 00:06:35,701
of the one who knows that's where we're heading okay so you can see there's a way of describing the human being from various different angles ayatana these powers and the final one would be datu or elements an element is something beyond which you cannot go it's your basic experience and that of course brings us to

68
00:06:36,425 --> 00:07:04,204
these four Mahabhutas the four great elements Bhuta actually means the four great beings but translated also as the Datu the Chattar or Datu which means the four great elements the last thing is this word Loka

