446
00:39:40,451 --> 00:39:43,981
And there's a sense of liberation from having to.

447
00:39:44,536 --> 00:39:52,083
having to try to squeeze blood out of a stone, having to try to get happiness from a piece of toast.

448
00:39:52,764 --> 00:39:56,568
It's like you see the stupidity of it.

449
00:39:57,530 --> 00:40:07,460
