00:40:09,262 --> 00:40:11,826
Another word for dispassion is contentment.

452
00:40:11,806 --> 00:40:12,567
That's it.

453
00:40:12,586 --> 00:40:15,411
So you don't need pleasant food to make you happy.

454
00:40:15,952 --> 00:40:28,092
So this begins to liberate us from this idea of having to have some sort of connection with food, undermining the connection of food with happiness.

455
00:40:30,797 --> 00:40:33,740
It doesn't at all undermine your sense of taste.

